大家好~我是南瓜~今天我又给大家搬运好东西啦~今天给大家带来的是一个128x的超细腻高清材质哟~
喜欢这种超清材质的千万不要错过哟！
目前已经更新到v1.1啦！
我也会永久更新这个材质的哟~

更新日志：

Replaced villager sound effects with silent tracks, leaving the death and hit effects unaltered so the default is used

Replaced the Creeper villager textures with Toad villager textures

*** Creeper villager textures & sound effects moved to a separate mini pack ***

Replaced the round compass texture with a new, square one

Redid the glowstone texture so it didn't look like a plain block of light

Revamped the Chain, Iron, Diamond and Gold armor models

Changed the armor hand-held item textures to something more generic and less obnoxious

Repaired the transparent edges on the crafting table and trap door

Changed the Steve skin to Toadie the Elf and added both the 1.7 and 14w versions

Changed the zombie texture to match the new Steve
